-- BHP May Boost Buyback Plan, Target Smaller Purchases, WSJ Says
-- B y   G r e g   C h a n g
-- 2010-11-15T21:53:48Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-11-15/bhp-billiton-may-boost-buyback-plan-target-smaller-purchases-wsj-reports.html
BHP Billiton Ltd. may boost the
amount of its share-buyback plan and target smaller
acquisitions, the Wall Street Journal reported, citing an
unidentified person.   The company may unveil specific policies on Nov. 16,
according to the report.   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
